These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, sudoku
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: house, salsa
There 2 different types of food: papaya, lime
2 different pets are kept: frog, turtle
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, vegafina
1. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1
2. the mechanic is on the far right##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the owner of the frog is the person eating lime##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | fanta     | cola       |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | sudoku     |
| Job           | fisherman | mechanic   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa   | house  |
| Food   | lime | papaya |
| Pet           | frog      | turtle     |
| Cigar     | vegafina    | siglo   |

