2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
6. the person who's birthday is in february is the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |
